HEADWORD: Metasternum
<hw>Met`a*ster"num</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>meta-</ets> + <ets>sternum</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>The most posterior element of the sternum; the
ensiform process; xiphisternum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The ventral plate of the third or
last segment of the thorax of insects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

